title: Moorhuhn - The Jewel of Darkness (Full)
description:
Guide the Moorhuhn through the numerous levels of the underworld, past the obstacles and defeat all the monsters as you go to advance to the next level. Try to collect all of the treasure as this will assure your place in the hi-score table. The small info-table gives you tips during the game so pay attention to it! In addition, you can choose which weapon to use yourself. If you cleverly deploy the falling blocks you can knock the monsters out of action but be careful not to block yourself in!

Key Game Features

145 action-packed levels!
Gold and precious jewels galore!
Every level a unique challenge!
